      "  Include what triggers it and whether it hard-blocks or is advisory.",
      "*/}",
      "",
      "| Policy | Enforced by | Trigger | Blocks commit? |",
      "| --- | --- | --- | --- |",
      "| [Rule description] | `operations/scripts/[script-name].js` | pre-commit | Yes |",
      "| [Rule description] | `operations/scripts/[script-name].js` | CI / manual | No (advisory) |",
      "",
      "Related policies:",
      "",
      "- [`docs-guide/policies/[relevant-policy].mdx`](/docs-guide/policies/[relevant-policy])",
